        { q: 'How much does a wedding videographer in Edmonton cost?', a: 'Wedding videography packages at MH Photography start at $3,750 for single-day coverage. Photo and video bundles start at $8,750. Multi-day Indian wedding videography packages are available with custom pricing based on the number of events.' },
